tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE feature_engineering_results (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    feature_1 FLOAT,
    feature_2 FLOAT,
    feature_3 FLOAT,
    target_variable FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE ModelEvaluation (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_id INT,
    metric_name VARCHAR(255),
    metric_value FLOAT,
    FOREIGN KEY (model_id) REFERENCES RegressionModel(id)
);

CREATE TABLE ModelParameters (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_id INT,
    parameter_name VARCHAR(255),
    parameter_value VARCHAR(255),
    FOREIGN KEY (model_id) REFERENCES RegressionModel(id)
);
